name: 3x Honey oats Goat's milk Soap without fragrances - Handmade in Germany - no more hand cream - regreasing - indenting
description: -Which soap?It is a gentle, re-greasing and moisturizing goat's milk oats honey soap with slight exfoliation efffekt through the oatmeal.-Phoenix soaps - production, ingredients and without fragrances:Our soaps are made in small batches exclusively manually by our freelancers in our factory and do not contain any preservatives or other chemicals; they are biodegradable.Our goat's milk, selected by local farmers, contains numerous vitamins such as:B12, B6, B1 and A as well as C&E minerals and caprylic acid, which are responsible for soothing the skin and are supposed to bring about a real makeover.Oatmeal as well as alpha-hydroxy acids (AHA) reduces wrinkles, signs of aging, peels the skin and are often used in expensive luxury cosmetics.Of course, our freelancer could have made the soap more beautiful, but he would have had to mix a lot of preservatives, perfumes and colors into it.This is exactly what he wanted to avoid and chose the natural soap, which also contains no fragrances.-well-maintained hands even in these times:At the moment we have to wash and cream our hands all the time.Due to the numerous washing processes in these times, our hands become leathery, cracked and stretching very often. Expensive creams need to be made to soothe the skin.Simply wash your hands with the honey oatgo goat's milk soap after each wash and you no longer need cream, the skin is sealed, soothed and nourished with a gently absorbing natural fat.- the soap may seem expensive to some, but it is still genuine handmade and without chemical additives.Only the natural ingredients that are indicated are used here, which means that you know exactly what is contained in the soap.- why the soap is not colorful:The brown color of the soap is automatically derived from the reaction of the goat's milk with the lye.All other goat's milk soaps that are not brown have colour additives, some and also with artificially produced mica powder, which has been chemically produced and consists of most of plastic.Here, artificial colours were deliberately dispensed with.- the soap becomes firmer the more often you use it and releases even more vitamins for the skin.- People with main problems have always given me positive feedback and are now regular customers.Stop lubricating chemical soaps on your skin, the ingredients of which you have not googled and whose effect on the skin you do not know.If you have any questions, you can contact us now and at any time.I am very happy to answer your questions.Packing:Delivery always 3 soap pieces / bars, approx.: 177 gr - we like to add something ;)

name: Windlight made of concrete, upcycling,wine bottle, jumbo, tealights, handmade,garden,party,wedding,decoration,birthday,gift.
description: A wind light made from a handmade concrete base as a base, in which both a normal or a jumbo tea light can be accommodated. A wine bottle cut by myself serves as a windscreen. The cutting surface is naturally ground to avoid injury. However, a possible slight ripple of the cutting surface cannot always be avoided!In the first few minutes, the wine bottle is briefly fogged from the inside, which is normal, after a short warm-up phase, the water vapor should have evaporated.The wind light has an approximate weight of approx. 1080g and is therefore very stable. The concrete base has of course undercut felt gliders to ensure protection against scratching of the surfaces on which the wind light stands. At the same time, the oxygen supply of the candle is ensured by a hole in the foot and the chimney effect.Half the glass bottle should be touched during operation if necessary, only at the extremely lower part as the upper one naturally gets hot.I have this windlight for all sorts of occasions like e.g. Weddings, birthdays designed for the garden or simply as evening underwriting in the house. name: Edison Concrete Lamp Solid | Retro Lamp | Steampunk | Cube | Concrete | Bedside lamp | Desk lamp | Industrial
description: An industrial-style lamp made of concrete in the form of a cube. It actually fits everywhere, as it doesn't seem so intrusive, but still interesting! In order to spare you the tedious search for a light bulb, I will deliver it immediately. You can choose between a right light bulb, not power saving (40watts) but absolutely authentic, or an LED with a power-saving 4 watt filament which also looks very great.Each lamp is unique and is handmade, enclosed bubbles at the edges are possible!!! Color deviations may occur.In addition, I chose a grey textile-wrapped cable with a simple cord switch to give the retro look even more prominence. name: Necklace Triskele Triple Spiral Wood Burned
description: Unique men's or ladies wooden necklace.Triple spiral(Druidism): Derived from the Greek word "Triskeles" meaning "three legs", the Triskele or Triple Spiral is a complex ancient Celtic symbol. Often referred to by many as a Triskelion, its earliest creation dates back to the Neolithic era, as it can be seen at the entrance of Newgrange, Ireland. The Triskele gained popularity in its use within the Celtic culture from 500BC onwards. This archaic symbol is one of the most convoluted to decipher as symbolists believe it is reflective of many areas of culture from the time.1)The motion of action, cycles, progress, revolution and competition.2)Life-death-rebirth, spirit-mind-body, mother-father-child, past-present-future, power-intellect-love and creation-preservation-destructionIt‚Äôs thought that through the combination of these two areas we gain one meaning of the Celtic triskele. It is believed to represent a tale of forward motion to reach understanding. However, this is thought not to be the only meaning, as it is also believed to represent three Celtic worlds; the spiritual world, the present world and the celestial world. Like the ancient Trinity knot, the number 3 holds a special symbolism within the triskele.Material:Wood: Beech WoodCord:  Cotton Waxed CordVarnish: Odorless Wood Varnish for children's toysApproximate Dimensions:Size:  35mm x 35mm x ~5mmCord Size: AdjustablePlease note that this item is handmade, so there may be small differences comparing with the photo.If you have any inquiries, please don‚Äôt hesitate to contact me. This includes being able to accept oneself and so the rose quartz can help lonely people to find in themselves the comfort and security that they have been denied in the outside. Rose quartz promotes empathy, which has a beneficial effect, especially in divorces or frequent disputes. Mistrust, fear, hatred and resentment dissolve and enable forgiveness. It makes it easier to accept others and themselves as they are and thus fosters a friendly atmosphere that is characterized by mutual respect. For this purpose, it is best to place a larger rose quartz chunk in the living/dining area or at the workplace. It should also not be missing in any children's room or living room of the elderly! Under the bed, it can help you get a better night's sleep.Just as the rose is the classic flower of love, rose quartz is the stone for all problems in the field of feelings, whether it is self-reproach or lack of respect for others or the environment. To be able to give love, I must first discard the (unconscious) conviction "I am not worth being loved" and begin to love myself. Only then can my love be visible in the outside.Physical effect:Radiaesthetic reviews showed that rose quartz positively affects relatively many frequencies. In particular, its effect in the area of the nervous system and in problems with the heart and blood circulation could be confirmed, probably due to the manganese content. It can be used well after a "mini-nerve collapse" because it supports strengthening and regeneration of nerves and also on the centers of healing, charity and responsibility.It also has frequencies in the area of digestion (feeling full, liver), acts on the skin (nails, warts, adipose tissue), the bone structure and the genital organs.The bracelet is with an elastic stretch band.
